  "title": "Facebook’s dating app bets we’ll trust them again",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 180.0,
      "end_time": 1970.0,
      "text": "- Facebook&#39;s F8 Developer Conference"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 1970.0,
      "end_time": 3920.0,
      "text": "started off on a somber note this year."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 4460.0,
      "end_time": 6700.0,
      "text": "Over the past two months, Facebook has been shaken"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 6700.0,
      "end_time": 9360.0,
      "text": "by the Cambridge Analytica data privacy scandal"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 9360.0,
      "end_time": 11700.0,
      "text": "which ultimately saw Mark Zuckerberg"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 11700.0,
      "end_time": 12790.0,
      "text": "called before congress to defend"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 12790.0,
      "end_time": 14639.0,
      "text": "Facebook&#39;s data collection practices."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 15400.0,
      "end_time": 17930.0,
      "text": "At the same time, critics are raising hard questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 17930.0,
      "end_time": 19939.0,
      "text": "about Facebook&#39;s impact on society"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 20270.0,
      "end_time": 22500.0,
      "text": "with some calling it a breeding ground"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 22500.0,
      "end_time": 23533.0,
      "text": "for misinformation and hate."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 24500.0,
      "end_time": 26170.0,
      "text": "Zuckerberg started F8 with a speech"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 26170.0,
      "end_time": 28120.0,
      "text": "that addressed those questions head on."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 28550.0,
      "end_time": 31800.0,
      "text": "- Now, I know that it hasn&#39;t been easy"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 31800.0,
      "end_time": 33890.0,
      "text": "being a developer these last couple of months"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 33900.0,
      "end_time": 35653.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s probably an understatement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 36550.0,
      "end_time": 40430.0,
      "text": "but what I can assure you is that we&#39;re hard at work"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 40590.0,
      "end_time": 43700.0,
      "text": "making sure that people don&#39;t misuse this platform"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 43700.0,
      "end_time": 45600.0,
      "text": "so you can all keep building things that people love."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 45600.0,
      "end_time": 47380.0,
      "text": "- In the midst of that crisis of trust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 47380.0,
      "end_time": 49640.0,
      "text": "Facebook is rolling out one of its most socially"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 49640.0,
      "end_time": 52807.0,
      "text": "ambitious project in years, a dating app."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 53240.0,
      "end_time": 55580.0,
      "text": "- We&#39;re announcing a new set of features"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 55900.0,
      "end_time": 58123.0,
      "text": "coming soon around dating."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 58613.0,
      "end_time": 61410.0,
      "text": "(audience cheers)"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 61410.0,
      "end_time": 63318.0,
      "text": "Now, this is gonna be for building"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 63319.0,
      "end_time": 67153.0,
      "text": "real long-term relationships, not just hookups."
