    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 83120.0,
      "end_time": 84559.0,
      "text": "- And I know a lot of you are gonna have questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 84559.0,
      "end_time": 86770.0,
      "text": "about this so I wanna be clear that we&#39;ve designed this"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 86770.0,
      "end_time": 89753.0,
      "text": "with privacy and safety in mind from the beginning."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 90550.0,
      "end_time": 92700.0,
      "text": "Your friends aren&#39;t gonna see your profile."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 93840.0,
      "end_time": 95290.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re only gonna be suggested people"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 95290.0,
